******************************************************************************************************

	Please write the instructions to run your code here

******************************************************************************************************
	- The dataset can be found in the data folders

	- The groundTruth directory contains the frame-wise labels for the videos (one file per video).

	- The features directory contains the frame-wise features for the videos (one file per video, and each file is a numpy array with dimension 2048xT).

	- In the following is a brief description of the files included in the data folder

		mapping.txt: List of the action classes and the corresponding id
	
		train.bundle: List of the training videos (Make sure to use the suitable path and extension to read the features or action labels)

		test.bundle: List of the testing videos (Make sure to use the suitable path and extension to read the features or action labels)
